<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هُجْنَةٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">التَّعْرِيفُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ا -<span class="c5"> مِنْ مَعَانِي الْهُجْنَةِ فِي اللُّغَةِ:</span> الْعَيْبُ وَالْقُبْحُ.<span class="c5"> يُقَال:</span> فِي كَلاَمِهِ هُجْنَةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَالْهَجِينُ:</span> مَا تَلِدُهُ بِرْذَوْنَةٌ مِنْ حِصَانٍ عَرَبِيٍّ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَالْهَجِينُ مِنَ النَّاسِ:</span> الَّذِي وُلِدَ مِنْ أَبٍ عَرَبِيٍّ وَأُمٍّ غَيْرِ عَرَبِيَّةٍ، وَالْجَمْعُ هُجُنٌ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلاَ يَخْرُجُ اسْتِعْمَال الْفُقَهَاءِ لِهَذَا اللَّفْظِ عَنِ الْمَعْنَى اللُّغَوِيِّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الأَْحْكَامُ الْمُتَعَلِّقَةُ بِالْهُجْنَةِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">يَتَعَلَّقُ بِالْهُجْنَةِ أَحْكَامٌ مِنْهَا:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أ -<span class="c5"> الْهُجْنَةُ فِي الْكَلاَمِ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> مِنْ آدَابِ الْكَلاَمِ:</span> أَنْ يَتَجَافَى الْمُتَكَلِّمُ هَجْرَ الْقَوْل وَمُسْتَقْبَحَ الْكَلاَمِ، وَلْيَعْدِل إِلَى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) لِسَان الْعَرَبِ<br>(٢) الْمَغْرِب، وَلِسَان الْعَرَبِ<br>(٣) رَدّ الْمُحْتَارِ ٣ / ٢٣٥</p> </div>